The paper proposes a deep learning approach for ECG classification, specifically using a recurrent neural network with bi-directional LSTM layers. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of recurrent neural networks also suggests a focus on neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions QRS detection, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV) and healthcare (cs.HC) applications.
